title: 820-00292 iMac 27-inch 2015 only 2 LED lights , Fan spins No chime.
message:
HI all,

This board has only 2 led light up no chime. Tried different rams no luck. 
All the power rails are present . cpu 12v FET gets 12 v. How ever Q8450 pin 4 FET_EN_P12V_S0_R is 24v. I dont kno is this correct volatge .

I have 2 logic boards same model same issue.

Any help greatly appriciate .

It is...

Did you test USB activity?
